# ğŸŒ€ Cassava Leaf Disease Classification with Convex CNN ğŸŒ€

This project implements a custom Convolutional Neural Network (Convex CNN) to classify cassava leaf diseases.  
The model was trained using transfer learning and optimized for robust performance on the [Cassava Leaf Disease Classification dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/cassava-leaf-disease-classification/overview) from Kaggle.

