## ğŸš€ Project Overview

Cassava is a staple crop in many tropical regions but suffers from several diseases that affect yield and quality.  
This project uses a lightweight CNN (Convex) architecture to classify cassava leaf images into disease categories with high accuracy.

Key features:

- âš™ï¸ Custom Convex CNN architecture  
- ğŸ§  Transfer learning applied where appropriate  
- ğŸ›ï¸ Data augmentation for improved generalization  
- ğŸ“ˆ Tracked training using loss, accuracy, and F1-score

